name: NFTboxTz 12 📦 💎 Kawaii cake 03
description:
Welcome to NFTboxTz 📦, where we release an NFT-filled grab bag with amazing, international artists. Each box is a low-priced 1/1 edition in comparison to the value of all the NFTs inside.

This is a one-time, NFT grab bag that, once purchased, content will be sent to the buyer and detached. Then the box is empty and becomes a cool collectible itself.

📦 Don't miss a drop! Follow us: https://twitter.com/NFTboxTz

🎨 Box art and 🎵 music by  Fabi Yamada (https://twitter.com/fabiyamada_art)
